parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPS system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult or impossible to turn, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The power steering assist warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes stiff or locks
the vehicle is difficult to steer
and the "Service Power Steering Now" or "Power Steering Assist Fault" message is displayed on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags can cause serious injury or death in the event of a crash.

sharp metal fragments may strike occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall has left many vehicles without a functional airbag system, putting occupants at risk of serious injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: manufacturer exceeding reasonable time for repair.
